JBOSS AS Tools integration
Updated for EAP 6.1

VisualVM
--------

Scripts to initialise visualvm with JBoss remoting libraries on classpath and run visualvm with JBoss remoting enabled


1) Install visualvm scripts: Copy visualvm.bat and visualvm.sh to $JBOSS_HOME/bin/

2) Execute visualvm script: 

	Linux; 
		2.1) execute $JBOSS_HOME/bin/visualvm.sh

	Windows;
		2.1) Set VISUALVM_HOME environment variable to base directory of visualvm 
		2.2) execute $JBOSS_HOME/bin/visualvm.bat



